page.title: 14GEORGIAN WORCESTER
page.content:
York Place
My name is Nicky Handley and I live in York Place.The houses are quite old. Most of them are one hundred and fifty to two hundred years old. Some have an out door toilet as well as a inside one.They are nearly all different.Sally's house is next door but one and it has a toilet down stairs and a big living room up stairs.We have the toilet up stairs and a smaller living room.Some have their kitchen up stairs.We all have an attic or a cellar but some use the attic as another bedroom.We all used to have shutters.
